title: Jeroen de Vaal,The Nightingale of Lexmond
description:
The Nightingale of Lexmond

Jeroen de Vaal,The Nightingale of Lexmond, was born September 14, 1973 in Utrecht.
Jeroen sang solos with several choirs in the Netherlands.Until Jeroen's voice 
changed at 15, he sang in nearly 300 concerts in and out of the country. He also 
sang on more than 20 LP's. As a boy soprano he wasn't only gifted with a beautiful 
clear voice but also a talent for music. Besides religious and classic songs he also 
sang international folk and musical songs. 

This torrent contains two of his albums 

Heer wat is Uw wereld mooi

The King of love my shepherd is
